<i>Any station this channel,</i>

42:39.223 --> 42:41.684
<i>this is Dolphin 3-6,
transmitting in the blind.</i>

42:46.772 --> 42:48.399
<i>Any station, this is Dolphin 3-6.</i>

42:48.399 --> 42:51.151
<i>We suspected comms failure.
Transmitting in the blind.</i>

